OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FVotes can be more than just votes and
OL,7,Fremain significant even if they don't
OL,8,Fimmediately change things. This week's
OL,9,FSenedd vote on childcare costs is a
OL,10,Fvery good example of that truth.
OL,12,FSenedd Members debated and voted on a
OL,13,Fmotion tabled by Reform UK leader Dan
OL,14,FThomas, "to ask the Welsh Government
OL,15,Fto publish the full costings and
OL,16,Ftimetable for the introduction of
OL,17,Ftheir childcare offer."
OL,26,@vD@IOUyD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/16
