OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FIt was designed to put pressure on
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru over the costings issue
OL,8,Fand was seen as something the
OL,9,Fopposition parties could unite on to
OL,10,Finflict an early defeat on the
OL,11,Fminority government.
OL,13,FIt wasn't to be. Despite Conservative
OL,14,Fsupport, the original motion fell
OL,15,Fbecause Labour voted with Plaid Cymru,
OL,16,Fthe Greens and the Lib Dems. Then the
OL,17,FConservatives voted for the amended
OL,18,Fmotion, meaning that the Plaid Cymru
OL,19,Fversion passed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FThat may seem like procedural detail
OL,7,Ffrom the Senedd chamber, but it tells
OL,8,Fus a huge amount about the direction
OL,9,Fof Welsh politics.
OL,11,FFirstly, it has acted as a reminder,
OL,12,Fif anyone needed one, that Rhun ap
OL,13,FIorwerth leads a minority government.
OL,14,FThe opposition parties may not have
OL,15,Fbeen able to defeat the government
OL,16,Fthis time, but they can - and will at
OL,17,Fsome point.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FThat reminder isn't unhelpful to the
OL,7,Fgoverning party either. Not that
OL,8,Fthere's any sign of dissent amongst
OL,9,FPlaid's euphoric MSs, but clearly
OL,10,Festablishing the threat should quell
OL,11,Fany nascent rebellions, no matter how
OL,12,Funlikely they seem right now.
OL,14,FIt has also shown Plaid that it faces
OL,15,Fa divided opposition, which it will
OL,16,Ftake as a hopeful sign: winning votes
OL,17,Fsuch as these is not necessarily the
OL,18,Fmost important thing, but not losing
OL,19,Fthem is.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FHowever, it can't count on that
OL,7,Fremaining the case forever. Sure, it's
OL,8,Falmost impossible to conceive of
OL,9,FReform UK, Labour and the
OL,10,FConservatives deliberately working
OL,11,Ftogether, but their interests will
OL,12,Falign on some issue at some point and
OL,13,Fthen there'll be no need for talks to
OL,14,Fget them to vote together.
OL,16,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV Wales, direct to
OL,19,Fyour inbox every Saturday morning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/16
