PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FReform UK Wales, under Dan Thomas'
OL,7,Fleadership, has already shown with
OL,8,Fthis vote that it's clever enough to
OL,9,Fidentify such a unifying issue. All
OL,10,Fopposition parties criticise Plaid
OL,11,FCymru for failing to produce costings
OL,12,Ffor its flagship policy or a timetable.
OL,14,FWhere it fell apart was down to
OL,15,Fdetails and politics, some of it
OL,16,Fseemingly personal.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
