OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FI understand that the Trefnydd (leader
OL,7,Fof the house) held conversations with
OL,8,Fboth Labour and the Conservatives to
OL,9,Fwarn them not to fall for what it
OL,10,Fdescribed as a "Reform stunt."
OL,12,FThere was no deal offered, something
OL,13,Fall three parties confirm, but Labour
OL,14,Fdenies there were any conversations at
OL,15,Fall.
OL,26,@rD@POUrD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/16
