CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FPlaid sources expected Labour to be
OL,7,Fmore receptive but were surprised by
OL,8,Fthe Conservatives' decision to support
OL,9,Fthe amended motion, something they put
OL,10,Fdown to bitterness and even 'hate'
OL,11,Ffrom the Tories towards Reform.
OL,13,FFor their part, the Conservatives say
OL,14,Fthat they were acting exactly as they
OL,15,Fsaid they would during the election
OL,16,Fcampaign, voting for whatever is in
OL,17,Ftheir manifesto (childcare was a
OL,18,Fpriority) and with whichever parties
OL,19,Fwould deliver things they see as
OL,20,Fimportant.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
