PN,43909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FThey supported Reform's original
OL,7,Fmotion and voted for both amendments
OL,8,Fbecause they wanted to back both the
OL,9,Fcall for costings and the importance
OL,10,Fof a childcare programme.
OL,12,FThey also say that Reform didn't talk
OL,13,Fto them and that, in the final vote,
OL,14,Fmore Reform MSs than Conservatives
OL,15,Fvoted for the Plaid Cymru amended
OL,16,Fmotion, either through confusion or
OL,17,Ffor other reasons.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
