CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FThat's not how Reform sees it. The
OL,7,Fparty's Chief Whip, Llyr Powell, wrote
OL,8,Fto Conservative leader Darren Millar,
OL,9,Fsaying that "I recall Members of your
OL,10,FGroup expressing concerns over the
OL,11,Flack of detail and potential cost in
OL,12,Fdelivering this policy. Natasha Asghar
OL,13,Foutlined her concerns on ITV's Sharp
OL,14,FEnd.
OL,16,F"I note your spokesperson, Sam
OL,17,FRowlands, said in the debate: 'If a
OL,18,Fpolicy is genuinely affordable, then
OL,19,Fpublishing those full costings should
OL,20,Fstrengthen confidence in it, not
OL,21,Fweaken it.'
OL,26,@oD@Ws|qD@MOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,451,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,F"Given your willingness to 'recognise
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Government's commitment to
OL,8,Fprovide an update on the initial
OL,9,Fcostings and phasing for the expansion
OL,10,Fof universal childcare' on their
OL,11,Fterms, is it now Welsh Conservative
OL,12,Fpolicy to give the Plaid Government a
OL,13,Fblank cheque on the implementation of
OL,14,Fall of their policies?"
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@WO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/16
