OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FMeanwhile, as part of the fallout of
OL,7,Fthe vote, we may be witnessing the
OL,8,Fbeginnings of a claim from Plaid Cymru
OL,9,Fthat could be a version of UK Labour's
OL,10,Fclaim after the 2024 General Election
OL,11,F- that the public finances were much
OL,12,Fworse that they appeared when the
OL,13,Fparty was in opposition.
OL,15,FRhun ap Iorwerth told LBC's Bronwen
OL,16,FWetherby that the Welsh Government has
OL,17,Finherited an 'incredibly tight
OL,18,Ffinancial situation, worse than people
OL,19,Fwould have imagined.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
