PN,43913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FI'm hearing similar in relation to
OL,7,Fchildcare. Sources have told me that
OL,8,Fbudgetary pressures have been made
OL,9,Fmore difficult by what they describe
OL,10,Fas the previous Labour government's
OL,11,Funfunded commitment on childcare.
OL,13,FWhat they're referring to is an
OL,14,Fincrease in the payment rate
OL,15,Fintroduced by the former Labour
OL,16,Fgovernment in April which they say has
OL,17,Fresulted in additional pressures on
OL,18,Fthe Childcare Offer, which was not
OL,19,Ffactored into the previous
OL,20,Fadministration's budgeting.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
