CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FLabour naturally rejects that. One
OL,7,Fsource says that the last Labour
OL,8,FFinance Minister was Mark Drakeford, a
OL,9,F"very upfront kind of person."
OL,11,FIt was he who brokered a budget deal
OL,12,Fwith Plaid Cymru last year, during
OL,13,Fwhich the party would have had sight
OL,14,Fof Welsh Government finances.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
