OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,FLabour sources also point to the
OL,7,Fparty's manifesto which states that
OL,8,F"The 2026-27 Final Budget does not
OL,9,Fallocate all the resources available
OL,10,Fto the Welsh Government. A small
OL,11,Famount of resource funding is left
OL,12,Funallocated to manage in-year
OL,13,Fpressures which will arise during 2026-
OL,14,F27.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
