PN,43916
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1781857088
OL,3,CWelsh Government: Are public finances
OL,4,Cmuch worse than they expected?
OL,6,F"The budget agreement included
OL,7,Fretaining #120m of capital funding
OL,8,Fwhich would be available for the next
OL,9,Fgovernment to allocate after the
OL,10,FSenedd election in May. This funding
OL,11,Fwill be available from the unallocated
OL,12,Fgeneral capital and further capital
OL,13,Fwhich will be made available during
OL,14,F2026-27 through in-year receipts"
OL,16,FWhether or not the new Welsh
OL,17,FGovernment pursues this approach will
OL,18,Fbecome clear soon enough. The Finance
OL,19,FMinister Elin Jones is making moves
OL,20,Ftowards introducing a supplementary
OL,21,Fbudget within the next few weeks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/16
